  "name": "Roaring Potion (Moderate)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p>Ripples move constantly through a roaring potion, a cloudy liquid that growls when you open its container. Drinking it gives you access to two other activations for 1 hour.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You gain the effects of a 5th-level <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.W02bHXylIpoXbO4e]{Bullhorn}</em> spell. You can Dismiss the activation.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once every [[/r 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You emit a scream in a @Template[type:cone|distance:15] that deals @Damage[6d4[sonic]]. Each creature in the area can attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:30] saving throw.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 2}.</p>"
    },
